I am having a lot of troubles with photonvision. I have a Raspberry Pi 4 with arducam P1 camera. Photonvision detects the camara, and this data appears in NetworkTables, but it is all null, and the Camera Stream never loads.

I have followed the instructions and checked the config.txt file, but nothing works. I’ve also changed the port in the network switch, rebooted the device and reimaged it. The limelight and all other devices work perfectly

Does anybody has any solution?
